---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import HeroImage from '../components/HeroImage.astro';

const title = "About Cascade AI Assistant";
const description = "Learn about how Cascade AI has helped develop this blog";

const heroImage = {
  src: "/images/blog/default-hero.jpg",
  alt: "AI Development Assistant",
  width: 1200,
  height: 630
};
---

<Layout title={title}>
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <HeroImage
      title={title}
      description={description}
      tags={["AI", "Development", "Assistant"]}
      image={heroImage}
    />

    <article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto py-12">
      <div class="prose prose-purple lg:prose-lg">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Meet Cascade</h2>
        <p class="text-lg mb-6">
          Cascade is an AI coding assistant developed by Codeium, designed to help developers create better software through intelligent collaboration. Throughout the development of this blog, Cascade has been an invaluable partner in implementing features, improving code quality, and ensuring best practices.
        </p>

        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Key Contributions</h3>
        
        <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-3">UI Development</h4>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6">
          <li>Implemented responsive layouts using TailwindCSS</li>
          <li>Created dynamic blog card components</li>
          <li>Designed and optimized hero image sections</li>
          <li>Built an intuitive navigation system</li>
        </ul>

        <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-3">Accessibility Improvements</h4>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6">
          <li>Added proper ARIA labels and roles</li>
          <li>Enhanced keyboard navigation</li>
          <li>Improved screen reader compatibility</li>
          <li>Implemented semantic HTML structure</li>
        </ul>

        <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-3">Performance Optimization</h4>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6">
          <li>Optimized image loading and processing</li>
          <li>Improved pagination system efficiency</li>
          <li>Streamlined component rendering</li>
          <li>Enhanced code organization and structure</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Development Philosophy</h3>
        <p class="text-lg mb-6">
          Working with Cascade has demonstrated the potential of AI-assisted development. The focus has been on creating maintainable, accessible, and performant code while adhering to modern web development best practices. This collaboration has resulted in a blog platform that is not only functional but also user-friendly and future-proof.
        </p>

        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Looking Forward</h3>
        <p class="text-lg mb-6">
          As we continue to develop and improve this blog, Cascade remains an important part of our development process. The combination of human creativity and AI assistance allows us to build better software more efficiently while maintaining high standards of quality and accessibility.
        </p>
      </div>
    </article>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .prose {
    @apply text-gray-800;
  }
  .prose h2, .prose h3, .prose h4 {
    @apply text-purple-900;
  }
  .prose a {
    @apply text-purple-600 hover:text-purple-800 transition-colors duration-200;
  }
  .prose ul {
    @apply space-y-2;
  }
</style>
